Watch as a dynamic fitness enthusiast performs energetic workouts, motivating you to stay active and healthy while you browse the web.

Features:
🏋️‍♀️ Fitness Animations: Watch a fit and determined character engage in various workouts.
🔍 Google Search Bar: Easily access your favorite websites with the integrated search bar.
🕒 Clock & Date Display: Keep track of time with the clock and date feature.
📌 Shortcuts Customization: Personalize your new tab with your most visited sites.
Why Download?
This Chrome extension is perfect for those who love fitness and want a constant reminder to stay motivated.
